snippet.textDisplay: JHUMUR is a traditional song of tea cultivated people in ASSAM. They are mainly ADIVASHI people. But their cultural heritage is very much richer than various tribal communities in ASSAM. Thanks to PAPON and SIMANTA for making this fusion and taking to modern standard. It will the mirror of mentioned community.
